@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = dev-key-please-rotate-in-production-0001

### Health check (anonymous)
GET {{host}}/health

### List the product catalog
GET {{host}}/api/products
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get a single product by id
GET {{host}}/api/products/456
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get a non-existent product → 404
GET {{host}}/api/products/does-not-exist
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Submit a batch of orders for aggregation
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

[
  { "productId": "456", "quantity": 5 },
  { "productId": "789", "quantity": 42 },
  { "productId": "456", "quantity": 3 }
]

### Submit with the secondary configured key
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: dev-key-please-rotate-in-production-0002

[
  { "productId": "456", "quantity": 1 }
]

### Missing API key → 401 Unauthorized
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "productId": "456", "quantity": 1 }
]

### Wrong API key → 401 Unauthorized
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: definitely-not-valid

[
  { "productId": "456", "quantity": 1 }
]

### Validation error (empty body)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

[]

### Validation error (invalid quantity)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

[
  { "productId": "456", "quantity": 0 }
]
